title: clusters_ejemplo
text:
Usage

Installation
Install latest from the GitHub repository:
$ pip install git+https://github.com/AzulEren/clusters_ejemplo.git
or from conda
$ conda install -c AzulEren clusters_ejemplo
or from pypi
$ pip install clusters_ejemplo


Documentation
Documentation can be found hosted on this GitHub repositoryâ€™s pages. Additionally you can find package manager specific guidelines on conda and pypi respectively.
